{"tid":1240361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭自作聰明,北京根本就唔care逃犯條例","createTime":"2019-06-18T10:17:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T12:19:14.000Z","uid":25345,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2a2afd8b117367dacc4eba5cb51b4cbed303ec47","tid":1240361,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T10:17:36.000Z","msg":"香港是中國與西方經商的重心，中國一直以香港「民心回歸」為長遠目標，但目前的大型示威，打擊了中國的計劃，亦令重挫中國想以香港作成功例子，實現收回台灣的目標。文章引述北京消息人士指，<span style=\"color: red;\">中央會樂見香港通過修例，但司法和執法單位並不認為有逼切性，從過去曾經有書商及商人不經香港的司法程序被帶到大陸可見，內地官員認為，即使沒有引渡條例，辦起事上來也沒有很大障礙。 </span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"260ccd2a7da80dd46a4d327ea58ee5a51aa905fc","tid":1240361,"uid":258598,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T10:18:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c0d380cea1dd6e29859ad696bae6d3678823e4ee","tid":1240361,"uid":120772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T10:19:03.000Z","msg":"唔緊要阿林鄭繼續堅持喇 可能真係港英餘孽嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75d81031bec80de338555825a526b3a0da397c6b","tid":1240361,"uid":189564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T10:19:08.000Z","msg":"識玩梗係玩廿三條<br />\n不過逃犯條例搞到玩唔到廿三條"},{"pid":"764da09ffa5073ff5a15af04f12c4b8864229c41","tid":1240361,"uid":25345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T10:20:13.000Z","msg":"大陸:有咪正式夾,冇咪背後夾囉,一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c22c5103166358d05847b6016a2481f9c26440cc","tid":1240361,"uid":71393,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T12:16:44.000Z","msg":"大陸: 錢呀我要錢呀"},{"pid":"0feb69441aa2d9f63639385096497c9210c